MIRIAMEntry
public interface Resource

Resource â€“ 2011.09.15
Identifier resource description of an identifier. Provides basic functionality such as Name, Definition and URL link. The internal URL should provide the address of an entry with the provided accession. The compiled pattern determines whether the accession patches the pattern for this resources identifier This class primarily serves as a mapping for a MIRIAM Registry entry
